                "help": "Value: One of cmuHFRCOFreq_1M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_2M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_4M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_7M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_13M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_16M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_19M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_26M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_32M0Hz, cmuHFRCOFreq_38M0Hz. Be sure to set hfrco-clock-freq accordingly!",
                "value": "cmuHFRCOFreq_32M0Hz",
                "macro_name": "HFRCO_FREQUENCY_ENUM"
            }
        },
        "core": "Cortex-M4F",
        "macros_add": [
            "EFR32MG12P332F1024GL125"
        ],
        "device_name": "EFR32MG12P332F1024GL125",
        "public": false
    },
